      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was out for a run in stanley park and i totally wiped out. my left ankle is huge right now and it's super swollen. i cant really walk on it at all without it hurting like crazy. i'm guessing i just sprained it lol. do u think i can just do the RICE thing for a few days and be fine? i really dont wanna go to the clinic if i dont have to",
